name: Xiao Tu / Rabbit
personality: She's mostly deaf, but once she sees you, will meow loudly for attention.
likes: Making friends with every person around, flopping at your feet to ask for pets. Giving paw for food.
dislikes: Any touch on her back. She also gets very annoyed when she sees another cat around and will start complaining.
other: Rabbit's carer states that she is around 18 years old. Her friendliness makes her beloved among all the neighbors, many of whom leave out food or comfy beds for her.
